data.title: Honda is impressed with Meggitt's crash sensor technology
data.meta_description: With over 5M cars sold last year, it is obvious Honda is recognized as a powerhouse in the automotive industry. It is a great honor that they have selected the Endevco 701A for their automotive crash testing application.
